{"tid":1615704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕者獲發還手機後，應如何處理","createTime":"2019-10-03T07:33:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T07:49:27.000Z","uid":277814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3abc0b218fd62eb49b4018c461eba14bdfcf02","tid":1615704,"uid":277814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:33:49.000Z","msg":"唔記得以前係邊度見到,或者有人用得著。當冷知識都好。<br />\n===========================================<br />\n不如都簡單形容下被捕者獲發還手機後，應如何處理﹕<br />\n<br />\n0. 被捕人士如果被提控，手機會作證物, 不會即時發還, 要審訊後才發還。<br />\n1. 無論如何，拿到手機後，唔好即用。<br />\n2. 出新sim card及新手機 (因硬件有單一IMEI号，可跟蹤)<br />\n3. 係電腦登入Google Account Security (<a href=\"https://myaccount.google.com/security\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmyaccount.google.com%2Fsecurity&d=2%2FeNT3TbtuwIHwt2a%2FmQGDIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=5eb32a4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://myaccount.google.com/security</a>)，檢查有否異常activitiy。改Google account password，一定要雙重認證。踢走原有手機, 令不能登入。<br />\n4. 改其他所有password，包括雲端、應用、媒體等等，亦看一下受制期間有冇被人login。<br />\n5. 檢查所有電郵設定，有無auto forwarding 及POP去你沒有設定的地址。<br />\n6. 開始裝新手機時，逐個apps做，唔好貪方便用手機過資料軟件。<br />\n7. contact list 檢查一下有冇新鬼。<br />\n8. 開舊手機時，唔好俾佢有網絡。冇sim card, 冇wifi。譬如熄咗屋企router和家人手機hotspot，disable 手機wifi後, 才開番屋企router。"},{"pid":"314c618fa475b7a66fe52709e18d217d05fcebf0","tid":1615704,"uid":304834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e94651947af6326b796832de80228aeeb5d763","tid":1615704,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3dc61af58f9e118f04abcbac707a9433117b342","tid":1615704,"uid":179004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:38:28.000Z","msg":"有用大家要cap底"},{"pid":"2701976ab1d164e4d881d694052843ffc9f57795","tid":1615704,"uid":266805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d939ae9391e89a892952ad70e228766855022f22","tid":1615704,"uid":324929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"有冇機會佢拆開你部機，裝d錄音裝置"},{"pid":"1d38293d814f1d7e4d1e798f14566f23575e03fd","tid":1615704,"uid":143400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T07:49:27.000Z","msg":"我輕接買左部部，拎左張新sim card，所有account改哂pw加用google remote erase舊機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}